  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "How do you know you're over your relationship?",
  "response": "Knowing that you're over a relationship can feel different for everyone, but here are some common signs that may indicate you've moved on:\n\n1. **You\u2019re Okay Thinking About Them Without Pain**  \n   You can recall memories of the relationship without feeling sadness, anger, or longing. The emotional charge is gone.\n\n2. **You Feel Neutral About Their Life**  \n   Hearing about their new relationships, successes, or life updates doesn\u2019t trigger jealousy, resentment, or strong emotions. You genuinely feel indifferent or even happy for them.\n\n3. **You\u2019ve Stopped Fantasizing About Reconciliation**  \n   You no longer imagine getting back together or wonder what they\u2019re doing. The idea of a future with them feels foreign or unappealing.\n\n4. **You Feel More Focused on Yourself**  \n   Your energy is directed toward your own growth, goals, and happiness rather than dwelling on the past or trying to figure out what went wrong.\n\n5. **You\u2019re Open to New Relationships**  \n   You feel ready to meet new people or explore romantic possibilities without comparing them to your ex.\n\n6. **You\u2019ve Accepted the Relationship Is Over**  \n   You\u2019ve come to terms with the end of the relationship and understand why it didn\u2019t work. You\u2019re no longer struggling to hold on or change the outcome.\n\n7. **You\u2019ve Built a Life Without Them**  \n   You\u2019ve created new routines, hobbies, and connections that don\u2019t revolve around them. Your sense of self is no longer tied to the relationship.\n\n8. **You Can Reflect on the Relationship Objectively**  \n   You can look back on the relationship with clarity, recognizing both the good and the bad, without being overwhelmed by emotion.\n\n9. **You Feel Relieved or Free**  \n   Instead of missing them, you feel a sense of relief or liberation. You realize the relationship wasn\u2019t serving you and that moving on was the right choice.\n\n10. **You\u2019re Excited About Your Future**  \n   Your focus is on what\u2019s ahead rather than what\u2019s behind. You feel optimistic about your life and the possibilities it holds.\n\nIt\u2019s important to remember that healing from a relationship is a process, and there\u2019s no set timeline. Being over someone doesn\u2019t mean you forget them entirely\u2014it just means they no longer hold emotional power over you. If you\u2019re still unsure, give yourself grace and time to heal fully.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
